snippet.title: Pathfinder: Kingmaker Features Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore! Conquer! Rule! Find out what Pathfinder: Kingmaker is all about in our brand new trailer! The first ever isometric cRPG set in Golarion is coming to you this summer.

Find out more at https://owlcatgames.com/

The voice artist in our video is Ray Chase
